    infrastructure    
      

IPA [ˈɪnfrəˌstrʌktʃɚ]
KK [ˋɪnfrə͵strʌktʃɚ]



 定義
 影片字幕 (1000)
 俚語 




解釋n.基礎設施；基礎建設；
例句The basic technology to support this method is the public key infrastructure (PKI).而基於非對稱加密體制的公鑰基礎設施(Public Key Infrastructure:PKI)為這種思路提供了最底層、最基本的支撐技術和手段。Cross-Disciplinary: Activities are coordinated through Board-level "Committee on Critical Infrastructure" and "The Infrastructure Security Partnership "組織：通過「重要基礎設施委員會」和「基礎設施安全合作夥伴協會」來協調活動。Infrastructure: In 2006, increase transportation infrastructure.基礎設施建設：2006年，加大交通基礎設施建設。A Privilege Management Infrastructure(PMI)system based on Public Key Infrastructure(PKI)technology, JSJYY-PMI, was developed.研發了一個基於公共密鑰基礎設施技術的許可權管理基礎設施系統。Expanding domestic demand, investment in infrastructure will increase, infrastructure, post-disaster reconstruction will start first.擴大內需方面，基礎設施投資力度將加大，其中基礎設施、災後重建將先行啟動。 




